name: SJS1: Streets Of Fear
description: A map I was planning to use in an 'expansion' for bloodrust that never really got anywhere, so instead I'm releasing it on it's own, as the first in a 'series' of single maps, that I may or may not release more maps for :P. Basically it's some kind of demon-overrun town (at least part of one). Also has a bunch of new textures and a new midi by me.
